[The swift actions and severe control measures applied by the Chinese
authorities, which follow the published detection of 3 suspected
human cases, underline the seriousness with which the Chinese
authorities view the current situation. Details of the performed
(negative) tests, carried out on the samples from the 3 human cases,
will be appreciated. The final results of the repeated tests,
reportedly to be performed in cooperation with WHO, are urgently
anticipated. - Mod.AS]
